      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-02827'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040513_GCR_179' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Amos</span> moved Amendment No. 61B:
        <q>Page 65, line 38, leave out "civil partnership to be registered" and insert "registration of the civil partnership to be recorded</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-02828'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040513_GCR_180' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
