          <p class='first-para'>
            I am happy to agree to do that. On that basis, I propose to move Amendments Nos. 61P
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_225gc' title='Col. 225GC &mdash; HL Deb 13 May 2004 vol 661 c225GC' name='column_225gc' href='#column_225gc' rel='bookmark'>225GC</a>
            to 61 AB, but make it clear to the Committee that, once I have circulated the notes on clauses, if it wants me to return at any point to answer further questions, I shall be happy to do so. I beg to move.
          </p>
